  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to demonstrate that platelet-derived repairing factors are
      effective and safe in the treatment of muscular lesion grade 2 or 3, a Phase II, open-label,
      single arm, single centre has been designed. Sample size will be 25.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
